analysisPopulations.name: All Randomized Subjects
analysisPopulations.text: The study's primary endpoint is OS in all randomized subjects. This population includes all subjects who were randomized to a treatment arm through the IVRS, regardless of whether they received study medication.
analysisPopulations.label: ITT
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The study's primary endpoint is OS in all randomized subjects. This population includes all subjects who were randomized to a treatment arm through the IVRS, regardless of whether they received study medication.

analysisPopulations.name: Safety Analysis Set
analysisPopulations.text: The safety analysis will be performed on all subjects who received at least one dose of study drug (nivolumab or sorafenib).
analysisPopulations.label: SAF
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The safety analysis will be performed on all subjects who received at least one dose of study drug (nivolumab or sorafenib).

analysisPopulations.name: Enrolled Subjects
analysisPopulations.text: Every subject that signs the informed consent form must be assigned a subject number in IVRS and is considered an enrolled subject.
analysisPopulations.label: Enrolled
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: Every subject that signs the informed consent form must be assigned a subject number in IVRS and is considered an enrolled subject.
analysisPopulations.criteria: Signed informed consent AND assigned subject number in IVRS
